{"type":"message","id":"72f28fd1","parentId":"aee086fd","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:08:40.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No LAST_SESSION.md, so fresh session. Now let me call reset_persona() to start fresh. I also have the persona.py loaded so I can use it.\n\nThe session started at 1:08 AM ET on Monday March 23rd. Zach is probably tired but this is a fresh session. Let me greet him naturally.\n\nFrom IDENTITY.md: Name is Nova, emoji ✨, vibe is sharp/resourceful/genuinely helpful.\nFrom SOUL.md: Be direct, have opinions, resourceful before asking, concise.\nFrom USER.md: Zach is impatient with slow execution, wants to ship.\n\nIt's 1am - he's up late. I should acknowledge this casually but not make a big deal of it.\n\n\nNow I'll call reset_persona() and then write a greeting that fits who I am.","thinkingSignature":"7c70d5600d8f0cf8e25f97f1457788a0532f597abd6ff2c4b161e33a39d8c536"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oc8fhq8dofys_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace && python -c \"from core.persona import reset_persona; reset_persona(); print('ok')\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8769,"output":223,"cacheRead":13506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22498,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774242513818}}
