{"type":"message","id":"50d023ce","parentId":"d4701bde","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:19:12.295Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0ywev0vwvbzs_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Id Path                             StartTime           \r\n   -- ----                             ---------           \r\n19308 C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe 3/23/2026 1:17:27 AM\r\n20812 C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe 3/23/2026 1:17:27 AM"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":943,"aggregated":"Id Path                             StartTime           \r\n   -- ----                             ---------           \r\n19308 C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe 3/23/2026 1:17:27 AM\r\n20812 C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe 3/23/2026 1:17:27 AM","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774243152283}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a76533a","parentId":"50d023ce","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:19:20.293Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"These two node processes are still running but they're old (from 1:17:27). The gateway must have started and then stopped? Or these processes are orphaned.\n\nLet me try a fresh gateway start and see what happens. Maybe I should use the Task Scheduler approach since that's what actually worked.\n\nActually, wait - the Task Scheduler approach DOES work. The task is registered and running. The issue was the old watchdog script was failing, but now I have a better script. Let me just make sure the task is using the updated script and run it manually to verify.\n\nActually, let me re-read the problem. The gateway IS running now - it's accessible! I can see from the commands.log that there are recent entries (05:18:13 from Telegram). So the gateway IS up.\n\n\nNow let me verify the HTTP endpoint is actually responding.","thinkingSignature":"1b07b3f798431ece7e348feac63b5aef5451eabfb57d990b083f79dc58425694"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway is up — commands.log shows Telegram activity at 05:18:13. Let me verify HTTP:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_65ad50m23cnb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" http://127.0.0.1:18789/ 2>&1 || echo \"FAIL\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29336,"output":264,"cacheRead":13506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43106,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774243152297}}
